1- go to terminal
2- use gitBash
3- run
   => $ curl -u Admin -p 12345(wrong)
   => $ curl -u Admin:12345 localhost:8080/home(correct)
   => -u = user (Admin)that you hava created in config/SecurityConfig
   => you must know about password case -> after typing user , use :pwd as -u Admin:12345
   => and then type url about your link ,
      it has localhost and port-number and direction that you have created in controller layer.

